resources.string: Thais app will attempt to make your "offline" gMusic available to all music players.
Make music available to stock music player.
Warning, this is an intensive task. You may get an option to "FC" or "Wait". This is normal, please choose wait and let the process finish.
Congratulations, your offline gMusic is now available to all music players. You will need to reboot or mount/unmount your sdcard for the media scanner to acknowledge the new tracks.
